, but still did not provide the specific numbers needed to calculate the difference in tertiary education completion by gender.\n</memory>\n\n<reflection>\nReflecting on the last action and its outcome, it appears that the task goal was not completed. \nThe last action was not successful in finding the specific numbers of men and women who completed tertiary education according to the 2011 Bulgarian census. \nAlthough the search results provided some general information about tertiary education and demographics in Bulgaria, they did not contain the necessary data to calculate the difference in the number of men and women who completed tertiary education. \nTo make progress toward the task goal, it would be helpful to try a different approach, such as extracting text from a specific URL that is likely to contain the needed information.\n</reflection>\n\n<plan>\nPlanning the next step based on memory and reflection, it would be helpful to try extracting text from a specific URL that is likely to contain the needed information. \nThe URL \"https://www.nsi.bg/census2011/pdocs2/census2011final_en.pdf\" from the google_search results appears to be a relevant document from the 2011 Bulgarian census. \nUsing the url_text_extractor tool to extract text from this URL might provide the necessary data to calculate the difference in tertiary education completion by gender. \nThis plan is helpful because it allows us to access specific information from a relevant source, which could lead to finding the needed data to complete the task goal.\n</plan>\n\n<action>\ntool: url_text_extractor\nparameters: {\"url\": \"https://www.nsi.bg/census2011/pdocs2/census2011final_en.pdf\"}\n</action>']\n\nYou are now at step 4.\nCurrent Observation: Tool 'url_text_extractor' executed.\nResult: {\n  \"url\": \"https://www.nsi.bg/census2011/pdocs2/census2011final_en.pdf\",\n  \"extracted_text\": \"%PDF-1.5\\r%����\\r\\n2057 0 obj\\r<\\n>\\rendobj\\r         \\r\\n2083 0 obj\\r<\\n>/Filter/FlateDeco